item.title: Comida Comunitaria del Vecindario
item.description: Sábado 30 de marzo de 2024 ¡ven a comer con tus vecinos! Trae tu plato internacional o americano favorito y disfruta de un tiempo de juegos y conversación mientras conoces a tus vecinos.

item.title: Over the Years
item.description: Through many years of planning, volunteering, and working together. We have a community that works together and growing with each other. Thank you everyone that has worked to build up this community over the years! … Our Sign Over the Years
